{
  "stem": "7016.1",
  "chunk_idx": 1,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I got all the-- I remember we used to have like a maid in the house when my mother was living.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Then she said, you're grown up.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "We don't need it.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And I have to do the work because I was-- so it was-- and then my father-- I've [? forgotten-- ?] married my mother, the two, my brothers, they-- one-- both left the house.",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "She said she doesn't want to have so many children at home.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "One went to my auntie, which my mother came the first time-- and my other brother went to his-- our uncle.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So the two brothers was not home, just I was with my brother.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And then, after the years, she got another three children.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And I-- I-- I-- I have to do all the work at home, like Cinderella.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And then we-- I finished school.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I finished seventh grade.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "This was-- to college in Europe was very hard to go.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I didn't got no opportunity just-- and I start to learn to be a [? seam make. ?] [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And then mine-- my stepmother, we got a food store for all kinds of food like you see here, from all-- all the other countries.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And the-- we-- I think they make the beautiful living that time.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Just my auntie, my mother's sister, used to come in the house.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And my brother, which she stayed-- my brother stayed with them, they always came in the house and they're so-- they wasn't happy that I washing dishes or peeling potatoes or raising her children.",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "I raised all the children.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So she said we-- that I want to live no more in Radomsko.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Then-- and we moved to Sosnowiec, and this was maybe two years before the war came out.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We moved to Sosnowiec.",
      "word_count": 4
    }
  ],
